 PALAISEAU, 15. Он женился на женщине по имени Guiburge De Montfort в 1210 г. в местности мирепоикс, ариeдж, окситани, Франция. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын и 1 дочь. Он умер декабрь 1230 г. в местности ла роше-бирнард, морбихань, бретагн, Франция в возрасте 50 лет и был похоронен в местности ваннесь, морбихань, бретагн, Франция."},"sm":{"1180–December 1230":"1180–Tesema 1230","1180–1230":"1180–1230","–Female":"Ua Maliu","1182–1234":"1182–1234","1210–Female":"1210–Ua Maliu","1230–Female":"1230–Ua Maliu","1210–1247":"1210–1247","1230–1284":"1230–1284","1155–1203":"1155–1203","1165–1210":"1165–1210","December 1230":"Tesema 1230","1165":"1165","1230":"1230","1284":"1284","15 janvier 1210":"15 Ianuari 1210","1182":"1182","1180":"1180","1203":"1203","1247":"1247","1234":"1234","1210":"1210","1155":"1155","about 1230":"e tusa o le 1230","Mirepoix, Ariege, France":"Mirepoix, Ariège, Farani","Lévis-Saint-Nom, Yvelines, Île-de-France, France":"Lévis-Saint-Nom, Yvelines, Île-de-France, Farani","Vannes, Morbihan, Brittany, France":"Vannes, Morbihan, Bretagne, Farani","Mirepoix, Ariège, Occitanie, France":"Mirepoix, Ariège, Occitanie, Farani","La Roche-Bernard, Morbihan, Brittany, France":"La Roche-Bernard, Morbihan, Bretagne, Farani"},"sk":{"1180–December 1230":"1180–december 1230","1180–1230":"1180–1230","–Female":"Zosnulá","1182–1234":"1182–1234","1210–Female":"1210–Zosnulá","1230–Female":"1230–Zosnulá","1210–1247":"1210–1247","1230–1284":"1230–1284","1155–1203":"1155–1203","1165–1210":"1165–1210","December 1230":"december 1230","1165":"1165","1230":"1230","1284":"1284","15 janvier 1210":"15. január 1210","1182":"1182","1180":"1180","1203":"1203","1247":"1247","1234":"1234","1210":"1210","1155":"1155","about 1230":"okolo 1230","Mirepoix, Ariege, France":"Mirepoix, Ariège, Francúzsko","Lévis-Saint-Nom, Yvelines, Île-de-France, France":"Lévis-Saint-Nom, Yvelines, Île-de-France, Francúzsko","Vannes, Morbihan, Brittany, France":"Vannes, Morbihan, Bretagne, Francúzsko","Mirepo